Prepare brownie mix according to manufacturers instructions for an 8x8-inch pan. Bake and let cool slightly. Place the DOVE Brand Miniatures in a mixing bowl and place the mixing bowl over a pot of simmering water. Stir the mixture as it melts. When mixture is shiny and smooth, turn off the heat. Pour half of the melted DOVE Brand Miniatures over the top of the brownies and set aside the remaining half. Sprinkle with 3/4 cup chopped SNICKERS Brand FUN SIZE Bars and 1 cup M&M'S Brand Dark Chocolate Candies for Halloween. Drizzle remaining DOVE Brand Miniatures on top. Let cool completely prior to serving.